'''Sah'c Town''', officially '''Quadrant H-46''' and also known as '''Sah'c District''', was an area on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It was named after the [[Sah'c family/Legends|Sah'c family]] that owned much of the quadrant and was said to be an unfashionable area of the [[Ecumenopolis/Legends|Ecumenopolis]].

Sah'c District was the location of a secure command bunker that the [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Supreme Chancellor]] was to be relocated to in case of an emergency or disaster. This bunker was connected by secure tunnels to [[500 Republica/Legends|''500 Republica'']], the [[Senate Building/Legends|Senate Building]], and the [[Republic Executive Building/Legends|Senate Office Building]].

Sah'c District contained [[Sah'c Canyon]], which was lined by skyscrapers and a maglev train rail and led to the Chancellor's emergency command bunker from the Senate District.

